name: Look Wanted
tag_list: social, beauty, apparel, discovery, wanted, looks, bloggers, fashionistas
overview:
Look Wanted is a website for creating and sharing detailed looks. It is currently in Beta.

It works in two ways: People can create a detailed look and share it with others; or people can upload a look’s picture and ask other users to help build it.

It is targeted at both look creators (Fashionistas, Trendsetters, Bloggers and Experts) and consumers who might want to know which product is in a certain look.

Visually it works like Pinterest. In its core, it works more like a Shazaam app, as it can be used for identification and discovery.
